snippet.title: Zork I: The Great Underground Empire - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Here is some gameplay of one of the most popular text adventures. Zork I originally debuted in 1981. It was more of an interactive story like a really old-school version of Final Fantasy. Had fun playing it even though I am not that good at it. Please post your comments and tell me what you think of my video.
You can play Zork I online at this site http://pot.home.xs4all.nl/infocom/zork1.html

Created by pulsar2121 games
